</groundspeak:short_description><groundspeak:long_description>nIce plAc_E espEciALl^y in WinT er -&amp;gt;LoTs of wilDLiFe, anD no huMans.
&lt;p&gt;caChe iS .30cAl aMmO CaN[[&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;hin#Ts:&lt;br /&gt;
tRai*l by WaTer&lt;/p&gt;
