&lt;p&gt;NOTE: The write-up above is the original from december 2000 and will be left that way BUT the walk to the cache is no longer considered to be a 1/1.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Park Entrance: N38 31.637 W75 29.035&lt;/p&gt;
