rking Area</type></wpt><wpt lat="49.278133" lon="-123.230667"><time>2011-01-11T23:30:08</time><name>T11DD</name><cmt>Recommended starting location</cmt><desc>Trailhead</desc><url>https://www.geocaching.com/seek/wpt.aspx?WID=228accf8-1494-442e-938f-f68311652daf</url><urlname>Trailhead</urlname><sym>Trailhead</sym><type>Waypoint|Trailhead</type></wpt><wpt lat="49.2753" lon="-123.232583"><time>2011-01-11T23:33:12</time><name>T21DD</name><cmt>Start of side trail (Look for pink flagging tape)</cmt><desc>Side Trail</desc><url>https://www.geocaching.com/seek/wpt.aspx?WID=d0291998-f6d5-4ca7-9a91-c16cbfa3eee8</url><urlname>Side Trail</urlname><sym>Reference Point</sym><type>Waypoint|Reference Point</type></wpt><wpt lat="49.2753" lon="-123.232967"><time>2011-01-11T23:34:28</time><name>T31DD</name><cmt>Treehugger (BC's First Cache)</cmt><desc>Location</desc><url>https://www.geocaching.com/seek/wpt.aspx?WID=e8e8c67d-b87a-4342-88c5-621128b244a8</url><urlname>Location</urlname><sym>Reference Point</sym><type>Waypoint|Reference Point</type></wpt><wpt lat="47.61783333333333" lon="-52.654333333333334"><time>2006-08-06T17:30:54</time><name>FLE1C</name><cmt>From the pit the container is ~47m distant, on a bearing of 302 deg true.</cmt><desc>The Lookout final</desc><url>https://www.geocaching.com/seek/wpt.aspx?WID=fb62dc15-0d9a-4c99-a12d-139f22d08fb9</url><urlname>The Lookout final</urlname><sym>Final Location</sym><type>Waypoint|Final Location</type></wpt><wpt lat="47.61755" lon="-52.65391666666667"><time>2016-01-23T12:39:07</time><name>S1E1C</name><cmt /><desc>GCE1C The Pit</desc><url>https://www.geocaching.com/seek/wpt.aspx?WID=a729c930-7799-4496-b5c2-44547eba66d5</url><urlname>GCE1C The Pit</urlname><sym>Reference Point</sym><type>Waypoint|Reference Point</type></wpt><wpt lat="52.20203333333333" lon="-107.00198333333333"><time>2015-08-08T16:48:10</time><name>PK14F</name><cmt /><desc>GC14F Parking</desc><url>https://www.geocaching.com/seek/wpt.aspx?WID=a9e934e7-22bc-4a01-8366-3514e2